            "text": "Name: CVE-2019-5482\nSeverity: Critical\nComponent: libcurl3\nType: Package vulnerability\nVersion: 7.52.1-5+deb9u8\nFixed version: 7.52.1-5+deb9u10\nSource: [CVE-2019-5482](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2019-5482)\nDescription: Heap buffer overflow in the TFTP protocol handler in cURL 7.19.4 to 7.65.3.",
