          "message": {
            "text": "Name: CVE-2017-8872\nSeverity: Critical\nComponent: libxml2\nType: Package vulnerability\nVersion: 2.9.4+dfsg1-2.2+deb9u2\nFixed version: 2.9.4+dfsg1-2.2+deb9u3\nSource: [CVE-2017-8872](https://security-tracker.debian.org/tracker/CVE-2017-8872)\nDescription: The htmlParseTryOrFinish function in HTMLparser.c in libxml2 2.9.4 allows attackers to cause a denial of service (buffer over-read) or information disclosure.",
